29
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:09,000
Then put up a goal and give it to reach it.

30
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:14,520
Before the stop. Don't go to the store if you are not going to shop.

31
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:20,520
Make sure to shop when you are measured. Make sure you really keep it.

32
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:24,880
It's a choice you make. It's your behavior.

33
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:28,000
What you do not consume today you can take advantage of tomorrow.

34
