47
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:23,760
This is the hardest thing for us humans.

48
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:27,160
We are used to having money, we get rid of them.

49
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:33,400
But it is deferred reward. You have to learn to see that there is a late.

50
