52
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:54,480
Do not go out in the stores to check for lunch.

53
00:03:54,560 --> 00:04:00,680
Do not google to look for the newest bags or clothes.

54
00:04:00,760 --> 00:04:04.920
Help yourself to fill your time with something else so that you do not end up in the temptation.

55
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:09.760
This is about a behavioral pattern that you have to change for you want.

56
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:13,040
Help yourself actually change it.

57
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:19,040
